1
00:00:02,320 --> 00:00:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That isn't Fushi!</font>

2
00:00:06,030 --> 00:00:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fushi and Yuki attempt to save Mizuha.</i></font>

3
00:00:12,090 --> 00:00:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Alas...</i></font>

4
00:00:15,260 --> 00:00:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fushi loses the vessel of the boy.</i></font>

5
00:00:21,570 --> 00:00:23,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, guys!</font>

6
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We defeat it!</i></font>

7
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:04,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="30" color="#291907">A Willingness to Believe</font>

8
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hell is your problem?!</font>

9
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's lock the door!</font>

10
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

11
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what are we doing in the science room?</font>

12
00:02:44,810 --> 00:02:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you looking for?</font>

13
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything we can use.</font>

14
00:02:53,090 --> 00:02:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found salt!</font>

15
00:02:54,430 --> 00:02:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What good is that going to do?</font>

16
00:02:56,260 --> 00:02:59,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought maybe it'd melt it, like a slug.</font>

17
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stupid. It's just going to get 
washed away by the sprinklers.</font>

18
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just avoid using fire.</font>

19
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're making use of it.</font>

20
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonari-san?</font>

21
00:03:12,330 --> 00:03:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found it!</font>

22
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing with that?</font>

23
00:03:17,090 --> 00:03:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to mix it with panko.</font>

24
00:03:20,090 --> 00:03:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what should we do?</font>

25
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make a barricade.</font>

26
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Draw its attention.</font>

27
00:03:25,060 --> 00:03:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Draw its attention?!</font>

28
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how?</font>

29
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get this over there.</font>

30
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this going to be enough?</font>

31
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish we had a little more.</font>

32
00:03:37,950 --> 00:03:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll need time.</font>

33
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So heavy.</font>

34
00:04:06,690 --> 00:04:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

35
00:04:12,740 --> 00:04:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's coming!</font>

36
00:04:13,930 --> 00:04:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it back!</font>

37
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dumbass! It's a pull door!</font>

38
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you just do?</font>

39
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, guys!</font>

40
00:04:40,570 --> 00:04:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you want to do this?</font>

41
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'll give it a try.</font>

42
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you on the rooftop in ten minutes.</font>

43
00:04:46,330 --> 00:04:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try what?</font>

44
00:04:47,970 --> 00:04:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, please come with me.</font>

45
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, very quietly...</font>

46
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tell you what we need to defeat it.</font>

47
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's split into two groups to gather it all.</font>

48
00:05:07,100 --> 00:05:09,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Defeat it? How?</font>

49
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no, no! There's no way!</font>

50
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:14,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, that Tonari girl isn't with us.</font>

51
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay.</font>

52
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonari-san is buying us time.</font>

53
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we need to defeat it?</font>

54
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagisa!</font>

55
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:23,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell us, quick!</font>

56
00:05:37,010 --> 00:05:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it! Follow me!</font>

57
00:05:40,770 --> 00:05:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fire. Fire.</i></font>

58
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fire. Fire.</i></font>

59
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Fire. Fire.</i></font>

60
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's that?!</font>

61
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The water makes it burn even more!</font>

62
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a tough one!</font>

63
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still have more!</font>

64
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Why?!</font>

65
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shoot!</font>

66
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shit! Sorry, let me go!</font>

67
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi!</font>

68
00:06:13,090 --> 00:06:13,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi!</font>

69
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something! Please!</font>

70
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi!</font>

71
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the metal sphere we used in Renril!</font>

72
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to let everyone know we're safe!</font>

73
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fire. Fire.</i></font>

74
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fire. Fire.</i></font>

75
00:06:43,050 --> 00:06:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't worry, Fushi.</i></font>

76
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can keep going!</i></font>

77
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi-sama!</font>

78
00:06:58,590 --> 00:07:00,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Reverend...</font>

79
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chami, ammo.</font>

80
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ammo!</font>

81
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-We're all out!</font>

82
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi-sama... I'm sorry.</font>

83
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

84
00:07:20,890 --> 00:07:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess not all Nokkers are the same.</font>

85
00:07:23,370 --> 00:07:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's go.</font>

86
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get you out of here.</font>

87
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reverend!</font>

88
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter? 
Aren't you going to fight back?</font>

89
00:07:36,010 --> 00:07:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to defeat you and 
give Mizuha back her father,</font>

90
00:07:40,170 --> 00:07:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I don't feel like doing it by force.</font>

91
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something wrong?</font>

92
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, no matter.</font>

93
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll play with you until you run out of ammo.</font>

94
00:08:03,140 --> 00:08:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, now. 
Lost your will to fight already?</font>

95
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no fun if you aren't 
at least trying to dodge!</font>

96
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

97
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't that I lost my will to fight 
so much as that I'm just interested now.</font>

98
00:08:18,590 --> 00:08:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want to know?</font>

99
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This Paradise that you were in...</font>

100
00:08:27,710 --> 00:08:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it like there?</font>

101
00:08:35,740 --> 00:08:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are there plants?</font>

102
00:08:47,820 --> 00:08:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Homes to shelter from the wind?</font>

103
00:08:57,130 --> 00:08:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A favorite chair?</font>

104
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A window that gives you a 
free view of the outside?</font>

105
00:09:07,070 --> 00:09:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Warm meals?</font>

106
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope Fushi-san can hold his own.</font>

107
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he can. He can do it.</font>

108
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, we're almost out.</font>

109
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang in there.</font>

110
00:09:34,070 --> 00:09:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What shall we do when we're home?</font>

111
00:09:36,490 --> 00:09:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First things first. A bath.</font>

112
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so hungry.</font>

113
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should come over.</font>

114
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Extraterrestrials welcome!</font>

115
00:09:46,430 --> 00:09:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might get invaded.</font>

116
00:09:48,450 --> 00:09:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi can make us as much bedding as we need.</font>

117
00:09:52,130 --> 00:09:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I mean.</font>

118
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:56,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have a common language.</font>

119
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can become friends.</font>

120
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe it.</font>

121
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A common language?</font>

122
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's cold!</font>

123
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! I'm drenched!</font>

124
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Mizuha.</font>

125
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dropped some water.</font>

126
00:10:15,470 --> 00:10:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Dad.</font>

127
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home.</font>

128
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

129
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got some new flowers delivered.</font>

130
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you love the colors?</font>

131
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the occasion?</font>

132
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're having Dad's favorite again.</font>

133
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but you love beef stew, too, Mizuha.</font>

134
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the kind of shit 
that makes you miserable.</font>

135
00:10:46,570 --> 00:10:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's delicious.</font>

136
00:10:53,070 --> 00:10:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, Yuki, we brought you some gifts.</font>

137
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we'll be off now.</font>

138
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be well, Yuki.</font>

139
00:11:01,140 --> 00:11:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

140
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leaving so soon?</font>

141
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay safe.</font>

142
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this, Yuki.</font>

143
00:11:20,890 --> 00:11:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hi, Yuki!</i></font>

144
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Have you been a good boy?</i></font>

145
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We may be far apart in body, 
but we're right there in spirit!</i></font>

146
00:11:35,130 --> 00:11:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vice President!</font>

147
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aoki-kun!</font>

148
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez! You could have told 
us you were struggling!</font>

149
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's not the time to be whining.</font>

150
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We gotta get back before sundown.</font>

151
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

152
00:11:49,010 --> 00:11:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or I won't make it home for dinner.</font>

153
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what you meant?</font>

154
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're being tested right now.</font>

155
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tested?</font>

156
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we believe?</font>

157
00:12:05,930 --> 00:12:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we do?</font>

158
00:12:10,650 --> 00:12:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have hope.</font>

159
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can understand each other's 
pain because we have bodies.</font>

160
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And our hearts can grow closer.</font>

161
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost ten minutes.</font>

162
00:12:33,290 --> 00:12:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here!</font>

163
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, the exit!</font>

164
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jump over!</font>

165
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it!</font>

166
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It worked!</font>

167
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got it!</font>

168
00:13:19,410 --> 00:13:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way...</font>

169
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we still in danger?</font>

170
00:13:28,650 --> 00:13:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shit...</font>

171
00:13:30,650 --> 00:13:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't dead!</font>

172
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

173
00:13:45,350 --> 00:13:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hell is that shit?</font>

174
00:13:47,250 --> 00:13:48,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

175
00:13:48,070 --> 00:13:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hell indeed.</font>

176
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Messar-san! Hairo-san! Kai-san!</font>

177
00:13:52,160 --> 00:13:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here to help!</font>

178
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know them?</font>

179
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're Fushi-san's friends!</font>

180
00:13:57,130 --> 00:13:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonari-san's Ligard came to let us know.</font>

181
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does Fushi know about this?</font>

182
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bon says he's headed 
where he should find him.</font>

183
00:14:07,230 --> 00:14:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can he make it on his own?</font>

184
00:14:09,470 --> 00:14:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems he isn't on his own.</font>

185
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lay a finger on the kids! I dare you!</font>

186
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My sword of justice will taste your blood!</font>

187
00:14:20,380 --> 00:14:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hirotoshi!</font>

188
00:14:22,070 --> 00:14:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who?</font>

189
00:14:22,830 --> 00:14:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go home, guys.</font>

190
00:14:26,260 --> 00:14:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, get on the bear!</font>

191
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't!</font>

192
00:14:35,930 --> 00:14:37,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't know when to quit.</font>

193
00:14:37,990 --> 00:14:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, go!</font>

194
00:14:39,470 --> 00:14:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

195
00:14:41,070 --> 00:14:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we really take it on without Fushi-san?</font>

196
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're taking it on.</font>

197
00:15:03,230 --> 00:15:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that supposed to do?</font>

198
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My sword didn't seem to be very useful.</font>

199
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it!</font>

200
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The water reservoir!</font>

201
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, shit! Run!</font>

202
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

203
00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:23,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Touch the water and you're dead!</font>

204
00:15:30,030 --> 00:15:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Avoid it, mister bear!</font>

205
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

206
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

207
00:15:35,950 --> 00:15:37,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the enemy?</font>

208
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No way!</font>

209
00:15:50,310 --> 00:15:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It revived?</font>

210
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apologies. We took it too far.</font>

211
00:15:59,150 --> 00:16:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonari!</font>

212
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

213
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi-san?</font>

214
00:16:16,770 --> 00:16:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonari-san!</font>

215
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're joking. Was that her?</font>

216
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's gotten into her?</font>

217
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Nokkers.</font>

218
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible!</font>

219
00:16:25,340 --> 00:16:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi-san already defeated all of them.</font>

220
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think about how he's been acting 
lately, and it'll make sense.</font>

221
00:16:31,050 --> 00:16:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's been happening 
when we weren't watching.</font>

222
00:16:34,210 --> 00:16:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been 500 years.</font>

223
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows how they might have evolved?</font>

224
00:16:40,050 --> 00:16:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have time to talk.</font>

225
00:16:42,110 --> 00:16:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna go?</font>

226
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not! She's one of ours!</font>

227
00:16:50,740 --> 00:16:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it!</font>

228
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?!</font>

229
00:16:56,230 --> 00:16:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's kill or be killed!</font>

230
00:17:12,950 --> 00:17:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Fushi-sama?</font>

231
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

232
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

233
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were too late...</font>

234
00:17:38,230 --> 00:17:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell is this?</font>

235
00:17:40,610 --> 00:17:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's that steel ball we used in Renril!</font>

236
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fushi?</font>

237
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We aren't Nokkers!</font>

238
00:17:48,290 --> 00:17:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Messar-san's locked in!</font>

239
00:17:51,450 --> 00:17:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-chan did it.</font>

240
00:17:53,470 --> 00:17:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? What do we do now?</font>

241
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look over there!</font>

242
00:18:09,910 --> 00:18:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's looking at us!</font>

243
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it coming?</font>

244
00:18:14,190 --> 00:18:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away! Stay away! Stay away!</font>

245
00:18:18,890 --> 00:18:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away! Stay away! Stay away!</font>

246
00:19:06,450 --> 00:19:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

247
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:08,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

248
00:19:08,490 --> 00:19:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. What happened?</font>

249
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's as if time has stopped.</font>

250
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're stuck.</font>

251
00:19:24,990 --> 00:19:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made it.</font>

252
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:31,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?</font>

253
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dunno.</font>

254
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no!</font>

255
00:20:07,940 --> 00:20:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't step in the water!</font>

256
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I remember him! Satoru!</font>

257
00:20:18,190 --> 00:20:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know him?</font>

258
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

259
00:20:20,340 --> 00:20:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was hanging out with Fushi-kun and, uh...</font>

260
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aoki-kun, from a year below us.</font>

261
00:20:25,850 --> 00:20:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Fushi?!</font>

262
00:20:27,710 --> 00:20:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Onii-chan?</font>

263
00:20:31,290 --> 00:20:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you bring that here?</font>

264
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Bring what?</font>

265
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, she moves.</font>

266
00:20:54,170 --> 00:20:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, then...</font>

267
00:20:55,340 --> 00:20:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What to do with you?</font>

268
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill you? Or...</font>

269
00:21:02,490 --> 00:21:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

270
00:21:05,210 --> 00:21:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please rest.</font>

271
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:08,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it easy.</font>

272
00:21:10,210 --> 00:21:12,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay.</font>

273
00:21:12,250 --> 00:21:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all okay now.</font>

274
00:21:13,820 --> 00:21:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's okay?</font>

275
00:21:17,730 --> 00:21:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me.</font>

276
00:21:20,930 --> 00:21:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stay here.</font>

277
00:21:23,360 --> 00:21:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stay and complete my duties 
as the head of the Guardians.</font>

278
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to live up to my 
ancestors' expectations.</font>

279
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you saying goodbye?</font>

280
00:21:34,270 --> 00:21:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to get us to hate you?</font>

281
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuha, I don't care where you stay,</font>

282
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if you want to finish your duties as the 
head of the Guardians, you'd better act quick.</font>

283
00:21:46,250 --> 00:21:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make the Nokkers stop messing 
with Fushi and getting bystanders</font>

284
00:21:50,350 --> 00:21:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">involved in your invasion, 
including by what they're doing at school.</font>

285
00:22:01,370 --> 00:22:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

286
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do what I can.</font>

287
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is there any kind of food you don't like?</font>

288
00:22:10,430 --> 00:22:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any allergies?</font>

289
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's gotten into you?</font>

290
00:22:14,060 --> 00:22:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's talk about the future!</font>

291
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For us and the Guardians!</font>

292
00:22:18,540 --> 00:22:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At my place!</font>

293
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over some hot pot or something!</font>

294
00:22:21,830 --> 00:22:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Us"?</font>

295
00:22:24,170 --> 00:22:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You trust us?</font>

296
00:22:27,990 --> 00:22:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what the past was like, 
we need to give the future a chance.</font>

297
00:22:33,090 --> 00:22:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to that crêpe shop again.</font>

298
00:22:36,330 --> 00:22:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to the Occult Club, too.</font>

299
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can go dowsing together.</font>

300
00:22:43,870 --> 00:22:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can trust you, right?</font>

301
00:22:46,490 --> 00:22:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you?</font>

302
00:24:29,980 --> 00:24:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="20">{\an8}Preview</font>

303
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In a moment of relief,</i></font>

304
00:24:34,450 --> 00:24:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the Guardians offer Yuki and the 
others a token of friendship.</i></font>

305
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the underground hollows, 
Fushi fights against the final resistance.</i></font>

306
00:24:45,630 --> 00:24:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His last remaining vessel</i></font>

307
00:24:49,090 --> 00:24:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>becomes the key to his awakening.</i></font>

308
00:24:52,010 --> 00:24:55,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="30" color="#291907">Clean Water</font>

